query:
SELECT b.siteId as booking_siteId, 
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM sites WHERE id = b.siteId) as exists_in_sites
FROM bookings b 
WHERE b.status = 'confirmed' AND b.startDate >= '2025-07-01' 
GROUP BY b.siteId
LIMIT 10;
